snippet.title: What ACTUALLY Happened at the Ambani Wedding
snippet.description:
Anant Ambani & Radhika Merchant's Pre-Wedding celebrations in Jamnagar where Mukesh Ambani spent more money than we'll ever earn - 1200 Crores.
We talk about all the khaatirdaari, hotels, food and the dance performances by ShahRukh Khan, Salman Khan & Amir Khan.
Rihanna & Akon ko bhi gava diya.

Follow us on Instagram -
Gautami - https://www.instagram.com/gautamikawale/
Abhyudaya - https://www.instagram.com/abhyudaya_mohan/

Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/slayypoint/
Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/SlayyPoint
Twitter - https://twitter.com/slayypoint

Subtitles by Nitika (available within 1-2 days of upload)

E-mail for BUSINESS ENQUIRES ONLY- slayypointofficial@gmail.com

Please don’t visit the pages/videos of any of these people to spread negativity nor to spam comments on their work, we all are just having some light-hearted fun that stays & ends here, no hate intended, ever!
Enjoy :)

snippet.title: MahaShivRatri 2024 Livestream with Sadhguru @ Isha Yoga Center | 8 Mar, 6 PM
snippet.description:
Celebrate Mahashivratri 2024 with Sadhguru on 8 March 2024, starting at 6 PM IST/12:30 PM GMT.

Mahashivratri is one of the largest and most significant among the sacred festivals of India and a night of immense spiritual possibilities for any spiritual seeker.

Contribute towards Mahashivratri activities and Maha Annadanam (a sacred offering of food) to devotees during the auspicious time of Mahashivratri: https://sadhguru.co/annam

#Mahashivratri2024 #AwakeWithAdiyogi #Mahashivratri #Live #AdiyogiLive #SadhguruLive  

Those who wish to enhance their receptivity to the auspicious period of Mahashivratri can participate in Pancha Bhuta Kriya with Sadhguru. The online program takes place on 8 March, before Mahashivratri.
Register at https://sadhguru.co/pbk-yt

Rudraksha Diksha is an opportunity to bring home the grace of Adiyogi by receiving a Rudraksha powerfully energized by Sadhguru on Mahashivratri night.
 Register now:  https://sadhguru.co/rd

Yaksha - an exuberant festival of Classical Music & Dance by world-renowned artistes - will take place from 5-7 March.

Transform Your Life in 7 Steps With Sadhguru Register now: https://sadhguru.co/ie-yt

"The Sadhguru Podcast -  Of Mystics and Mistakes   (Listen Now on)"
https://open.spotify.com/show/69ZUhdV0q2JtibNU2yLTpQ

Get access to rare Sadhguru content on Sadhguru Exclusive. Choose from a variety of series that cover the mystical, intense, intimate and candid.
Watch Now: https://sadhguru.co/exclusive

Official YouTube Channel of Sadhguru

Considered among India’s 50 most influential people, Sadhguru is a yogi, mystic, bestselling author, and poet. Absolute clarity of perception places him in a unique space, not only in matters spiritual but in business, environmental and international affairs, and opens a new door on all that he touches.

Inner Engineering 

Inner Engineering is a comprehensive course for personal growth that brings about a shift in the way you perceive and experience your life, your work, and the world that you live in.

https://innerengineering.sadhguru.org/

Isha Life products for everyday health and well-being. Buy online at https://bit.ly/3L0gTar

Save Soil Movement

Launched by Sadhguru, Save Soil is the world's largest people's movement, reaching 3.91 billion people to address impending soil extinction by supporting governments to create policies for soil revitalization.

https://savesoil.org/

Sadhguru app 

Accelerate your spiritual journey with transformative guided meditations, daily wisdom, and Yogic tools.

http://onelink.to/sadhguru__app

snippet.title: Aadujeevitham - The Goat Life  Official Trailer A R Rahman, Prithviraj Sukumaran, Amala Paul, Blessy
snippet.description:
Presenting the most-awaited #TheGoatLifeOfficialTrailer of the greatest survival adventure and desert film #TheGoatLife - Aadujeevitham

From National Award-Winning Filmmaker Blessy comes an extraordinary tale adapted from the best-selling novel ‘#Aadujeevitham’ by Benyamin. 

The movie, based on a true-life incident, is set to release in theatres worldwide on 28th March 2024.

The trailer is just a glimpse of the hard-hitting story that awaits your presence, with extraordinary visuals and soul-stirring music to give you a breathtaking cinematic experience in Malayalam, Hindi, Tamil, Telugu, and Kannada.

 #TheGoatLifeOn28thMarch 
----------------------- 

Here's more on #TheGoatLife

Produced by: Visual Romance
Directed by: Blessy
Screenplay by: Blessy
Based on: Aadujeevitham by Benyamin
Music by: A. R. Rahman
Cast: Prithviraj Sukumaran, Amala Paul, Jimmy Jean-Louis, KR Gokul, Talib Al Balushi and Rik Aby.
Edited by: A. Sreekar Prasad

—---------------------
Be a part of The Goat Life journey on:

👉Website - thegoatlifefilm.com
👉Instagram - instagram.com/thegoatlifefilm
👉YouTube - youtube.com/@VisualRomanceOfficial
👉Facebook - facebook.com/AaduJeevithamFilm
👉X (formerly known as Twitter) - twitter.com/TheGoatLifeFilm

snippet.title: Hall Ticket | Episode 1 - Planning, Preparation aur Pressure | Mini Series | Take A Break
snippet.description:
In this gripping episode of "Hall Ticket," we follow Ujjawal, a young boy on the brink of his 10th board exams, as he grapples with the weight of expectations and the looming pressure of his impending exams. 📚💥
Join us as we witness Ujjwal's struggle transform into a tale of resilience and motivation. Through hard work, perseverance, and the unwavering support of his loved ones, Ujjawal discovers that the power to succeed lies within himself.

Discover the world of 'Hall Ticket,' a series capturing the ups and downs while preparing for board exams. Join us as we follow students through late-night study sessions and last-minute reviews, sharing their nerves and excitement. 

____________________________________

Khumar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

Khumar is a timeless love story that delves into the challenges arising from societal class differences and the negativity that stems from them. Khumar explores the complexities of love in the face of societal expectations and challenges. Faiz and Hareem, two individuals from different backgrounds, find their lives connected by destiny.

Faiz, born into an affluent family, contrasts sharply with Hareem, who hails from a
lower-middle-class background. Despite their differences, fate weaves their paths together. Hareem, diligently working to make ends meet amid her brother Rufi's educational needs and her mother's medical expenses, faces numerous hurdles. In the midst of her struggles, Faiz, a friend of Rufi's, silently supports them financially and even gets work for Hareem, albeit discreetly.

Hareem's family doesn't know that Faiz loves her, leading to a one-sided love affair. Faiz's love for Hareem remains a secret, but his mother disapproves of his association with Hareem's family due to the significant class difference. But fate decides to play its tune, and an unexpected event turns the lives of Faiz and Hareem upside down.

What was this surprising turn of events that changed everything for Faiz and Hareem? Will the gap in their social status keep them apart? Can Faiz convince his mother to accept Hareem? If they marry, can they create a happy life together despite their different backgrounds and mindsets?

snippet.title: Master 11 vs Khiladi 11 | Highlights | ISPL | 6th March 2024
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony LIV Channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/sonyliv
 
Click here to watch all highlights: https://bit.ly/3OVl9LM

Click here to watch more: https://www.sonyliv.com/sports/cricket-indian-street-premier-league-1700001390

Click here to subscribe now: https://bit.ly/3Q78rHU

Watch the highlights of the inaugural match between Sachin Tendulkar's Master 11 and Akshay Kumar's Khiladi 11 in the Indian Street Premier League 2024. Sachin Tendulkar's Master 11 scored 94 runs in 10 overs and lost 7 wickets in the process. Sachin was the top scorer with 30 runs. Akshay Kumar's Khiladi 11 then put up a strong performance during the chase but lost the match by 5 runs in the end. 

Master 11: Sachin Tendulkar, Amir, Suresh Raina, Yusuf Pathan, Stuart Binny, Rishabh Chavan, Munaf Patel, Ram Charan, Kunal Khemmu, Samir Kochhar, Elvish Yadav.

Khiladi 11: Akshay Kumar, Suriya, Irfan Pathan, Robin Uthappa, Praveen Kumar, Naman Ojha, Gaurav Taneja, Prateik Babbar, Sukhwinder Singh, Munawar Farooqui, Riyaz Ali.

प्रधानमंत्री नरेंद्र मोदी (pm modi) ने आज कई युवा हस्तियों को नेशनल क्रिएटर्स अवॉर्ड से  सम्मानित किया...भारत मंडपम (National Creators Award 2024) में आय़ोजित कार्यक्रम में पीएम मोदी ने कथावाचक जया किशोरी  (Jaya Kishori) से लेकर मैथिली ठाकुर (maithili thakur) सहित कई युवा हस्तियों को सम्मानित किया...ये अवॉर्ड 20 से अधिक कैटेगिरी में दिए गए है... इनके लिए करीब 1.5 लाख नॉमिनेशन मिले थे। वोटिंग राउंड के दौरान विनर्स का सिलेक्शन करने के लिए लगभग 10 लाख वोट डाले गए। इसके बाद तीन इंटरनेशनल क्रिएटर्स (National Creators Award live) समेत 23 विजेताओं का चुनाव किया गया

snippet.title: குணா குகையின் அறிவியல் மர்மம் என்ன? 🤯 Guna Cave Secrets 😱 Manjummel Boys | Mr.GK
snippet.description:
The Guna Caves, dating back to 1821, were initially discovered by British officer B.S. Ward, only to fade into obscurity until their rediscovery in the 1990s, showcasing their natural beauty.
குகைகள் அதன் மோசமான வரலாற்றிற்கு அறியப்படுகின்றன, ஏனெனில் ஆய்வுக்காகச் சென்ற பலர் குகைக்குள் ஒரு தடயமும் இல்லாமல் காணாமல் போயுள்ளனர், மேலும் சில சமயங்களில் குகை அமைப்பு மிகவும் ஆழமாகவும் சீரற்றதாகவும் இருப்பதால் அதிகாரிகளால் அவர்களின் உடல்களை மீட்டெடுக்க முடியவில்லை. 2016 ஆம் ஆண்டு நிலவரப்படி, உடல்கள் மீட்கப்படாமல் குகை தொடர்பாக 16 பேர் காணாமல் போனதை போலீசார் பதிவு செய்தனர். 

00:00 - Intro
01:10 - Guna Cave
03:32 - How do Caves form?
04:20 - Types of Caves
08:24 - Archaeological Importance
10:00 - Caves and Acoustics
10:43 - Cave Research Foundation
11:50 - Why Caves are Dangerous
14:35 - Nutty Putty Cave
15:35 - Tham Luang Cave Rescue

WhatsApp: https://whatsapp.com/channel/0029VaA23u5IHphLuhO3LM01
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/MrGKTamil
Twitter: https://twitter.com/Mr_GK_Tamil
Instagram: http://instagram.com/Mr_Gk_Tamil

snippet.title: "Too much is said about Bazball" 🗯️ | Nasser Hussain reacts to England Test series loss to India

Official “we can’t be friends (wait for your love)” Lyrics:
i didn’t think you’d understand me how could you ever even try
i don’t want to tiptoe
but i don’t wanna hide
but i don’t want to feed this monstrous fire
just want to let this story die and i’ll be alright
we can’t be friends
but i’d like to just pretend
you cling to your papers and pens wait until you like me again
wait for your love
love
i'll want for your love
me and my truth we sit in silence baby girl it’s just me and you cause i don’t wanna argue
but i don’t wanna bite
my tongue yeah i think i'd rather die
you got me misunderstood but at least i look this good
we can’t be friends
but i’d like to just pretend
you cling to your papers and pens wait until you like me again
wait for your love
love
i'll want for your love
know that you made me
i don’t like how you paint me yet i’m still here hanging
not what you made me something like a daydream but i feel so seen in the night so for now it’s only me
and maybe that’s all i need
we can’t be friends
but i’d like to just pretend
you cling to your papers and pens wait until you like me again
wait for your love
love
i'll want for your love

Episode 4028: Surprise Party For Popatlal
--------------------------------------------------------
Gokuldham residents and Popatlal's colleagues kidnap Popatlal and take him to his surprise party. Abdul reveals why he switched sides and became a part of Tapu Sena's plan. Popatlal tells everyone why he didn't want to celebrate his birthday with them. 

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 4028, 9 Mar 2024
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Aar Ya Paar In Haridwar - Stand-up Comedy By Sundeep Sharma
snippet.description:
It's a nostalgic story from my teenage years. Young and stupid make the interesting story tellers later in life. I hope I am not wrong. This video is about my Haridwar visit with my parents and siblings and my teenage bravado. I have performed this bit for a few years, I am hoping that you like it. Please do share this video and subscribe to my channel. Do leave a comment :) 

Credits: 
Venue courtesy: The Habitat-Comedy and Music Cafe
Directed by: Balraj Ghai
Edited by: Ankit
Shot by: Dishang Popat, Vivian Castelino Harsh Shah and Karan Kundnani
Live sound recording: Yash Rajiv Barse, Siegen Moopnar
Sound mixing and mastering: Sreejith Menon
Written and performed by: Sundeep Sharma 

Special Thanks: Pictures and video footage of Haridwar: Garima Lohumi
Sonam Priya for inputs
Emina Singh for the quote in the beginning and being a patient ear
Saurabh Pandey for being the constant support
My babies Alpha and Beta for being the reason I work and go to work like Papa Bear.
&
My Mother for being the constant support and playing a character in my story here. 
My Father for being the man he was and always inspiring me to do better and never give up.

snippet.title: Rakesh Barot | તને રડવા ના દેશુ | Tane Radva Na Desu | Gujarati New Song 2023 | નવું ગુજરાતી ગીત
snippet.description:
આવો તૈયાર થઈએ રાકેશ બારોટના નવા ગુજરાતી ગીત "તને રડવા ના દેશુ" માટે, ફક્ત @SaregamaGujarati  પર 💜

Singer: Rakesh Barot
Artist: Rakesh Barot, Palak Patel 
Producer: Red Velvet Cinema
Concept & Director: Shankar Thakor Borisanawala 
Creative Head: Dhyey Films & Team
Technical Support: Jenish Talaviya
Lyrics: Vipul Raval
Music: Mayur Nadiya
Co Artist: Vina Tank, Navya Khamar, Satubha Thakor, Babusinh Thakor 
Makeup Man: Chirag Parmar 
Hairdresser: Manisha 
Production Manager: Satubha Thakor 
Assi. Director: Babusinh Thakor 
Lights: Kalpesh Jadav 
Spot Boys: Gunvant Kaka, Bhavarsinh
Dop: Arvind Motap 
Video Editing: Kishor Rajput 
Dubbing: Sv Studio 
Poster Design: Aman Angola

Lyrics:

હો દુઃખ ના દરિયામાં અમે ડૂબી જઈશું...(2)
પણ તને કદી દુઃખી ના કરશું
હા અમે રડી લેશું અમે રડી લેશું
તને રડવા ના દેશું...તને રડવા ના દેશું

હો તારી દરેક વાતે સમંત અમે રહેશું
તું ના પાડે એ રસ્તે ના જઈશું
હા અમે રડી લેશું અમે રડી લેશું
તને રડવા ના દેશું...તને રડવા ના દેશું

હો પાંપણ તારા પલળે દુઃખ થાય મારા દલડે....(2)
હા અમે રડી લેશું તને રડવા ના દેશું
હા તને રડવા ના દેશું
 
હો બોલ્યા પછી વાલી અમે બીજું બોલતા નથી
તારા કોઈ વાત ને અમે ટાળતા નથી
ઓ તારું મુખ જોયા વગર દિવસ જાતો નથી
તને જોયા પછી મારો હરખ હમાતો નથી

હો તારી દરેક વાતે સમંત અમે રહેશું
તું ના પાડે એ રસ્તે ના જઈશું
હા અમે રડી લેશું અમે રડી લેશું
તને રડવા ના દેશું...તને રડવા ના દેશું

તને પ્રેમ કરું અનહદ તને પ્રેમ કરું હરપલ
પ્રેમ કરું અનહદ તને પ્રેમ કરું હરપલ
હા અમે રડી લેશું તને રડવા ના દેશું
હો તને રડવા ના દેશું

હો દુનિયા ની બધી ખુશી આપવા માંગુ તને
દુવા મારી ફળી આજ મળી ગઈ તું મને
હો મારી સાથે રહેશો તો સ્વર્ગ લાગશે તને
મન માં ના વિચારો કઈ દ્યો ને હવે

હો તારી દરેક વાતે સમંત અમે રહેશું
તું ના પાડે એ રસ્તે ના જઈશું
હા અમે રડી લેશું અમે રડી લેશું
તને રડવા ના દેશું...તને રડવા ના દેશું

હો મારો પ્રેમ તમે સ્વીકાર્યો મળ્યો જન્મો નો સથવારો...(2)
હા અમે રડી લેશું તને રડવા ના દેશું...તને રડવા ના દેશું
તને રડવા ના દેશું...તને રડવા ના દેશું


Ho Dukh Na Dariya Ma Ame Dubi Jaishu...(2)
Pan Tane Kadi Dukhi Na Karishu
Ha Ame Radi Laishu Ame Radi Leshu
Tane Radva Na Deshu...tane Radva Na Deshu

Tane Radva Na Deshu...tane Radva Na Deshu

Tane Radva Na Deshu

Ho Bolya Pachi Vali Ame Biju Bolta Nathi
Tara Koi Vaat Ne Ame Talata Nathi
O Taru Mukh Joya Vagar Divas Jato Nathi
Tane Joya Pachi Maro Harakh Hamato Nathi

snippet.title: Bhide ने लगाया Jump और जा भिड़ा दीवार से | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah| Bhide - Madhavi Specials
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBIT1FSJW6yTlzqK-31FDWg?sub_confirmation=1

When Bhide sees an old radio in a junk dealer's shop, he falls in love with it and expresses interest in purchasing it. Bhide and the Scrap Dealer strike a profitable bargain. Will Bhide find success in the old radio, or will it cause him, Madhvi, and Sonu a great deal of trouble? 


Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 1259
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2024 #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #jethalal #tarakmehta 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Surprise Baby Shower 🤰 ♥️
snippet.description:
Little did I know there was a surprise 🤰 Baby Shower coming up for me. 
I have always seen and enjoyed watching baby showers through videos. But this was one of the best and the most memorable days of my life. 
Mastermind or the planner was Jeema, a kind-hearted follower of mine who turned out to be a very dear and close friend. Coordinated with the rest of my friends. Her cute home-baked mommy Cake. I didn’t want to cut it as it was too cute to look at. And her son Jain who joined was a silent partner ♥️
Nifla, as usual with her amazing food and drinks. Shilja with her home-baked brownies which I couldn’t get a photo of as it got over soon. Sneha, Naina, and Shilja with their lovely gift from Victoria’s Secret.

It was such a surprise cum shock to see this coming. I can’t get over it as I am still in the shower mode 😃….
Thank you my dear ladies for this cute sweet and most memorable day in my life. I will cherish this forever 😍😍😍😍

@niflaub @naina170390 @menon3020 @shiljavinay & Jeema ♥️
.
.
.
#surprise #babyshower #bestday #friendsforever #memorable

snippet.title: शिवरात्रि व्रत की थाली-कम घी से बनी 6 रेसिपी में से जो चाहे बना लीजिये | Mahashiv Ratri Vrat Recipes
snippet.description:
Shivratri vrat prasad recipes, Shivratri menu , Shivratri vrat recipes, Shivratri fasting food, Shivratri special dishes, Shivratri vrat meal, Shivratri fasting thali, Shivratri vrat ki recipes, Shivratri vrat ka khana, Shivratri vrat food ideas
#vratkakhana #vratrecipe #shivratri #fastingfood 

Ingredients for Shivratri Vrat Thali
For Singhare ki katli
गुड़ - Jaggery - 1/2 cup (100 grams)
घी - Ghee - 2 tbsp
सिंघाडे़ का आटा - Water chestnut flour - 1/2 cup (75 grams)
For Gajar Makhana Kheer
घी - Ghee - 1 tbsp
मखाने - Fox nut - 1/2 cup
घी - Ghee - 1 tbsp
गाजर - Carrot - 2 no, grated
दूध - Milk - 1/2 litre, fullcream
बादाम - Almonds - 1 tbsp
काजू - Cashew - 1 tbsp
इलाइची - Cardamom - 4 no, crushed
चीनी - Sugar - 3 tbsp
For Aloo Tamatar Sabzi
घी - Ghee - 1 tbsp
जीरा - Cumin seeds - 1/2 tsp
टमाटर - Tomato - 1 no
हरी मिर्च - Green chilli - 1 no
अदरक - Ginger - 1/2 inch
काली मिर्च - Black pepper - 1/4 tsp, crushed
आलू - Potato - 3 no (250 grams), boiled
सेंधा नमक - Rock salt - 1/2 tsp
हरा धनिया - Coriander
For Fruit curd
दही - Curd - 1.5 cup
अंगूर - Grapes - 1/2 cup
अनार - Pomegranate - 1/2 cup
सेब - Apple - 1 no
चीनी - Sugar - 1 tsp
किशमिश - Raisins - 1 tbsp

For Chutney
हरा धनिया - Coriander - 1 cup
हरी मिर्च - Green chilli - 2 no
अदरक - Ginger - 1/2 inch
सेंधा नमक - Rock salt - 3/4 tsp
जीरा - Cumin seeds - 1/2 tsp
काली मिर्च - Black pepper - 1/4 tsp, crushed
नींबू का रस - Lemon juice - 1 tbsp
For Sama Rice pancake
समा के चावल - Sama rice - 1/2 cup
आलू - Potato - 2 no (200 grams)
अदरक - Ginger - 1/2 inch
हरी मिर्च - Green chilli - 2 no
काली मिर्च - Black pepper - 1/4 tsp, crushed
सेंधा नमक - Rock salt - 1/2 tsp
हरा धनिया - Coriander - 1 tbsp

snippet.title: GOAT BLOOD FRY | Traditional Goat Blood Recipe Cooking In Village | Goat Blood Gravy with Intestine
snippet.description:
Today in our village, We cook our village's traditional goat blood recipe by making blood gravy and blood fry. We call this recipe as "Raththa Koottu" and "Raththa Poriyal". We add some goat internal parts to goat blood gravy, such as the liver, lungs, and intestine.

Finally, we enjoy the food with our favourite muttun curry! The taste is delicious!

snippet.title: Maha Shivarathri Special rangoli designs 2024 || Simple Pandaga muggulu || easy Festival kolam
snippet.description:
Maha Shivarathri Special rangoli designs 2024 || Simple Pandaga muggulu || easy Festival kolam
It is our tradition to draw kolam every day morning at the doorsteps.
There are many benefits of drawing kolam in front of the house.
It is auspicious and believes Goddess Lakshmi enters the house if kolam is drawn.
Kolam brings a lot of positive vibrations and energy to you and your home.
Draw kolam soon after you wake up and then do your prayers.
Kolam or rangoli ( रंगोली  ) is a part of Indian culture and transferred from generation to the next generation.
This ancient art form is also called as muggulu in parts of South India like Andhra Pradesh and Telangana.
People draw different creative rangoli kolam designs using kolam powder or muggu pindi which is 
actually crushed Lime stone powder available in different parts of India.
There are different types of rangoli or kolam designs like dots kolam, sikku kolam, padi kolam, Margazhi kolam.
People draw special rangoli designs for Festivals like Sankranthi (Pongal), Diwali (Deepavali), Vijaya Dashami (Dasara).
Women create deepam rangoli or kolam designs during Diwali festival time, create very big and Dhanurmasam muggulu (Margazhi) for Sankranthi or Pongal festival.
It is a belief among the people that drawing muggulu in front of the house in the early morning soon after wake brings
good fortune to them and their family.
People mix rice flour to limestone powder and prepare their own kolam powder. Muggulu can also be drawn with rice flour only.
These Beautiful and creative designs are decorated with flowers based on the occasion or festival.
